The 2019 Data Storage, Backup and Recovery Conference took place at The Venue in Melrose Arch on 13 March 2019. The emcee for the event was Radio 702’s Aki Anastasiou, who was joined by Siatik CEO Brett StClair, Commvault’s Johan Scheepers, and VMware’s Ian Jansen van Rensburg. Other speakers at the event included SensePost CTO Dominic White, CipherWave MD Wayne D’Sa, and Microsoft’s cloud and enterprise lead Johannes Kanis and audience developer Rory Preddy. The conference was possible thanks to the excellent sponsorships from Commvault, Gabsten Technologies, VMware, Cibecs, and ContinuitySA. Photos of the event are posted below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-299254 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference020-640x427.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference020-640x427.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference020-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference020-768x512.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference020.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-299256 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference035-640x427.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference035-640x427.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference035-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference035-768x512.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Data-Storage-Conference035.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: